OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome early brightness in the
OL,6,Feast, otherwise another rather grey
OL,7,Fstart with some patchy light rain or
OL,8,Fdrizzle. Remaining largely cloudy this
OL,9,Fafternoon but a few bright or sunny
OL,10,Fspells will develop. Winds tending to
OL,11,Fstrengthen later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry initially this evening,
OL,14,Fbut a band of wet and windy weather
OL,15,Fwill sweep across the region
OL,16,Fovernight. Rain clearing east towards
OL,17,Fdawn allowing some clearer spells to
OL,18,Fdevelop.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
