OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA brighter day tomorrow
OL,6,Fwith a mix of cloud and sunny spells.
OL,7,FThe odd light shower is possible but
OL,8,Fmost will be dry with winds easing.
OL,9,FTemperatures around average.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FUnsettled and windy on Thursday with a
OL,13,Fband of heavy rain arriving later.
OL,14,FColder with some blustery showers on
OL,15,FFriday, before turning drier and less
OL,16,Fcold on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
